); const CompanyProfilePage = ({ handleNavigation }) => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const coreValues = [ { icon: Shield, title: "Integrity", description: "We operate with transparency and honesty in all business dealings." }, { icon: Rocket, title: "Excellence", description: "We strive to deliver top-quality services that consistently exceed expectations." }, { icon: Handshake, title: "Commitment", description: "Dedicated to client satisfaction and continuous improvement in service delivery." }, { icon: Users, title: "Teamwork", description: "We believe collaboration is key to achieving collective goals and greater success." }, { icon: Lightbulb, title: "Innovation", description: "Continuously improving processes and training for better, more efficient service delivery." }, ]; const industries = [ { name: "Oil & Gas", icon: Globe }, { name: "Construction", icon: Building2 }, { name: "Hospitality", icon: Handshake }, { name: "Logistics", icon: Briefcase }, { name: "Healthcare", icon: Users }, ]; const teamMembers = [ { name: "John Doe", role: "Managing Director", desc: "15+ years of leadership in manpower and logistics solutions." }, { name: "Sarah Ahmed", role: "HR Operations Lead", desc: "Expert in overseas recruitment and workforce management." }, { name: "Mohammed Ali", role: "Project Coordinator", desc: "Oversees client projects and ensures timely manpower deployment." }, ]; return (
{/* Hero Section */}

Our Company Profile

Excellence in Manpower Solutions. Recognized for reliability and innovation in workforce management.

{/* Company Overview */}

ARM Group specializes in providing skilled manpower on a rental and local transfer basis, as well as managing large-scale recruiting from overseas to meet diverse client requirements across multiple industries.

Industry Focus: Oil & Gas, Construction, Hospitality, Logistics, and General Services.

  • Founded in 2010 with a mission to provide reliable workforce solutions.
  • Served over 150 corporate clients across GCC and Asia.
  • Average contract completion rate of 98% with consistent client satisfaction.
{/* Vision & Mission Section */}

Our Vision

To be the leading manpower solutions provider recognized for excellence, reliability, and innovation in workforce management.

Our Mission

To deliver qualified, trained, and motivated manpower that drives our clients' success while fostering growth, safety, and satisfaction among our dedicated workforce.
